title: Inspiring Wish
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

Once per day, you can fervently wish for something you could work towards achieving as a single action which has the <<tag Concentrate>> trait. 

If you do, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus on the first skill check you attempt before the end of your turn to fulfill that wish.